title: SwifTEA: Dr. Taylor Swift's Commencement Speech!
description:
She delivered the best commencement speech of all time.. Dr. Taylor Allison Swift gave the graduating class of NYU these words of wisdom!
Plus, is there a new date to clown over and what actually happened on 5/13?
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
